Content: Read this if you have ever felt alone_ depressed_ suicidal_ lost_ scared_ worthless_ abandoned_ or anything of that nature_ this is for youNLNLNLNLNLNLYou Are Beautiful.NLYou Are Wanted.NLYou Are Wonderful.NLNLDon't quit on yourself. Don't hurt yourself. You are worth the world and nobody wants to see you suffering. This is not the end. The way you feel right now will pass. Peoples minds will change. Things WILL get better.NLWe love you and are always here for you. Do NOT do something permanent over something temporary. NLYou're better than that.NLAll stars need to see darkness before the light.NL    And always remember_ Don't change so people will like you. Be yourself & the right people will find and love the real you.NLNLYourNLownNLuniqueNL NLMindsetNLalwaysNLtrysNLtoNLengage  in theNLright   waysNLNLNow read the first letter of every wordNLNLYou Matter! no matter what other people may say. Always know this is true. It helps. You are worth my time to write this. I do care. ❤ Continue on ❤ be a soldier. Fight that war. Because YOU can. I believe in you. I'm rooting for you! Good luck!NLNLPlease pass this on to other videos! ❤️❤️❤️
